WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.200
But if you let me know something happened to my brother

2
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.300
I will definitely let you go.

3
00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:08.366
Don't be afraid, as long as you listen to me obediently

4
00:00:08.366 --> 00:00:11.300
Your brother's bone marrow transplant and post-treatment

5
00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:13.233
I'll arrange it for you.

6
00:00:14.933 --> 00:00:17.633
So, when can I speak to my brother?

7
00:00:18.533 --> 00:00:20.066
He hasn't seen me for so long

8
00:00:20.366 --> 00:00:22.300
I'm afraid he will worry about me.

9
00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:30.433
Come here.

10
00:00:31.766 --> 00:00:32.766
Do you hear me?

11
00:00:32.766 --> 00:00:34.100
I asked you to come over.

12
00:00:36.466 --> 00:00:37.266
Wait a minute.

13
00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:41.900
Miss Lin is so proactive

14
00:00:42.166 --> 00:00:44.066
You are in front of other men

15
00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:45.966
Are you also so proactive?

16
00:00:46.566 --> 00:00:48.866
Since Mr. Gu looks down on me so much

17
00:00:48.866 --> 00:00:51.500
Why do you have to keep me by your side?

18
00:00:51.533 --> 00:00:54.400
I said you are my thing

19
00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:55.666
My stuff

20
00:00:56.466 --> 00:00:58.200
Even if you don't like it

21
00:00:58.900 --> 00:00:59.700
Then I have to come too

22
00:00:59.700 --> 00:01:00.666
No, you're not.

23
00:01:00.900 --> 00:01:01.966
I warn you.

24
00:01:01.966 --> 00:01:04.300
I'm in a bad mood today, if you have any more

25
00:01:05.766 --> 00:01:09.000
I can't guarantee what will happen to sleep

26
00:01:11.733 --> 00:01:14.566
Guo Yiming, that beast

